\pard\f0\fs20 Le mod\&#39;e8le physique de donn\&#39;e9es sinistres fait appara\&#39;eetre les grands groupes de donn\&#39;e9es suivants :\f1\par
\f0 - les sinistres : identifiants et informations principales des sinistres, qu&#39;ils soient rattach\&#39;e9s \&#39;e0 un contrat d&#39;acceptation (fac ou trait\&#39;e9), un programme ou un contrat de r\&#39;e9trocession\f1\par
\f0 - les montants de sinistres : montants attach\&#39;e9s aux sinistres, qu&#39;ils soient comptables ou non, et class\&#39;e9s par position successives identifi\&#39;e9s par une date et une devise\f1\par
\f0 - les montants de sinistres \&#39;e0 un niveau global : montant \f1\par
\f0 - les informations techniques d\&#39;e9taill\&#39;e9es des sinistres \f1\par
\f0 - les \&#39;e9v\&#39;e9nements : au niveau groupe et au niveau filiale\f1\par
\f0 - les \&#39;e9l\&#39;e9ments de niveau section : ils servent \&#39;e0 la comptabilisation de montants globalis\&#39;e9s au niveau section apr\&#39;e8s saisie individuelle par sinistre\f1\par
\f0 - l&#39;historique de montants : permet de conserver l&#39;\&#39;e9volution mensuelle des montants au niveau des sinistres et des \&#39;e9v\&#39;e9nements\f1\par
\par
\par
2013-10-14 / Omega2-Phase 2B-TRT29\par
Creation of new table (duplicate of the BTRAV..TESTSECTION) to store the attachment contract number.\par
\par
2013-10-29 / Omega2-Phase 2B-TRT29\par
TESTSECTION table name modified: FRATTACHEVOL\par
\par
2013-11-07/ Omega2-Phase1B\par
- Added SITE_CF and ID_NF columns to TREQJOB and TREQJOBPLAN tables\par
\par
2013-11-22/ Omega2-Phase2A-TRA01\par
- Added  \par
SGT_NT  : Segmentation ID of the Segmentation linked to the Closing Version\par
SGTVER_NT : Version number of the Segmentation linked to the Closing.\par
\par
2013-12-10/ Omega2-Phase2B\par
- SGLA06: added TRN_NT to store Detailed Transaction Code (new primary key replacing ACMTRS_NT &amp; PRS_CF) on TLIFEST table\par
- EST50: added GAAP_NT &amp; DIFF_M to manage values by GAAPs on TLIFEST table\par
- SGLA03: added ACM_NF (wave 2C modification done in advance) to take into account monthly values on TLIFEST table\par
- EST24: added RETCTR_NF, RETSEC_NF, RETUWY_NF  (wave 2C modification done in advance) to indicate associated retro contract on TLIFEST table\par
\par
2013-12-10/ Omega2-Phase2B-EST50\par
- Added GAAP number column in TLIFMOD2 table\par
\par
2013-12-10/ Omega2-Phase2B-SGLA03\par
- Added Accounting Month (ACM_NF) added to the primary key on TLIFEST table\par
\par
2014-01-10/ Omega2-Phase2B-SGLA06\par
- Modified code of Detailed transaction code (DETTRNCOD_CF) in TLIFEST table\par
\par
2014-01-24/ Omega2-Phase2B-EST50\par
- Added PROPAGATION_B boolean to store propagation preferences in TLIFEST table\par
- Batch: added BATCH_B boolean to indicate when a line has been created or updated by batches in TLIFEST table\par
\par
2014-01-31 / Omega2-Phase 2B-TRT29\par
FRATTACHEVOL Table name modified: TRATTACHEVOL\par
\par
2014-01-31/ Omega2-phase2B-EST47\par
- Four columns added in TCTRULT : CMTLR_NT, CMTWP_NT, WPLSTUPDUSR_CF, LRLSTUPDUSR_CF\par
\par
