- Added ORIGAAP_CT column to TLIFEST table\par
\par
2014-02-10/ Omega2-Phase2B-SGLA06\par
- Added CALCULATED_B column to TLIFEST table\par
\par
2014-02-24/ Omega2-Phase2B-EST39\par
- Added (SEGUPD_B) the boolean that indicates if a segmentation update has been done in TLIFDRI table.\par
- Added (RESPROPAG_B) the boolean that indicates if modifications on reserves should be propagated on future accounting years in TLIFDRI table.\par
\par
2014-04-11/ Omega2-phase2B-EST47\par
- Removed columns WPLSTUPDUSR_CF, LRLSTUPDUSR_CF\par
- Added column EGPILRMODIF_CF\par
\par
