- Creation of the table TELIGIBILITY that stores eligibility rules\par
\par
2014-04-28/ Omega2-Phase2B-EST Life\par
- TLIFEST: Reordering of columns + use of bit type for booleans\par
- TLIFEST: Removed ORIGAAP_CT column\par
- TLIFNEWBIZ: Removed BALSHEY_NF and BALSHTMTH_NF columns\par
\par
