<a:Description>{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg1252\deff0\deflang1036{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset0 Times New Roman;}}
{\*\generator Msftedit 5.41.21.2510;}\viewkind4\uc1\pard\f0\fs20 2013-05-29 / Omega 2-Phase 1B&#39;-OM-B-TRA01\par
- Creation\par
\par
2013-06-17 / Omega 2-Phase 1B&#39;-OM-B-TRA01\par
- last update fields become mandatory\par
- added MAXLVL_NB field to support segment hierarchy management.\par
\par
2013-06-25 / Omega 2-Phase 1B&#39;-OM-B-TRA01\par
- added SSD_CF field to attach a Subsidiary to the Segmentation. \par
- update banal codifications\par
\par
2013-06-25 / Omega 2-Phase 1B&#39;-OM-B-TRA01\par
- Change type of SSD_CF to SSD_CF instead of char(3)\par
\par
2015-01-20 / Omega 2-Phase 2B&#39;-TRA01\par
- Merge SEG datamodel into EST datamodel\par
\par
2017-03-30/ CR 34674\par
Addition of Update Comment\par
}
</a:Description>
