<a:Creator>U001107</a:Creator>
<a:ModificationDate>1584624853</a:ModificationDate>
<a:Modifier>U008652</a:Modifier>
<a:Comment>Indicates how the Segment is managed by the &quot;Balai&quot; feature (i.e. non balai, balai for external or internal assumed, facultatives, non proportional treaties, proportional treaties). Default is &quot;Non Balai&quot; and other values are possible only if the related Segmentation supports the &quot;Balai&quot; feature (BALAI_B field set to True). Should match a valid entry of the SGTBALAITYP_CF banalised codification (TBANAL).</a:Comment>
<a:DataType>char(5)</a:DataType>
<a:Length>5</a:Length>
