\par
2013-06-17 / Omega 2-Phase 1B&#39;-OM-B-TRA01\par
- last update fields become mandatory\par
\par
2013-06-25 / Omega 2-Phase 1B&#39;-OM-B-TRA01\par
- add one level to Max Hierarchy Level (max 5)\par
\par
2015-01-20 / Omega 2-Phase 2B&#39;-TRA01\par
- Merge SEG datamodel into EST datamodel\par
\par
}
</a:Description>
