<o:Table Id="o336">
<a:ObjectID>CE7DB3C2-60C8-4C78-A13F-3B1D5BAD63BA</a:ObjectID>
<a:Name>Segmentation Type Rule Usage</a:Name>
<a:Code>TSEGMENTRULE2TYPE</a:Code>
<a:CreationDate>1422954629</a:CreationDate>
<a:Creator>U001107</a:Creator>
<a:ModificationDate>1584624853</a:ModificationDate>
<a:Modifier>U008652</a:Modifier>
<a:Comment>This table tracks all Segmentation Types used as criteria in Segment Rules.
These elements enable to track dependencies between Segmentations.
Rules may use only Segmentation Types of lower Processing Order (see PROCESSORD_NT field of the TSEGTYPE table).
Entries are automatically added/removed upon modification of each Rule definition.
</a:Comment>
<a:TotalSavingCurrency/>
