<a:CreationDate>1422954629</a:CreationDate>
<a:Creator>U001107</a:Creator>
<a:ModificationDate>1584624853</a:ModificationDate>
<a:Modifier>U008652</a:Modifier>
<a:Comment>A Criteria Category provides a first level of grouping for Segmentation Criteria used in the Segment Rule editor.
A Category is supported on specific Portfolio Scopes (i.e. Assumed and/or Retro contracts), see TSEGCRISCOPE.
It is further split into Criteria Sub-Categories and does not contain directly the Segmentation Criteria.</a:Comment>
<a:TotalSavingCurrency/>
