<a:Name>Segmentation Criteria Sub Category</a:Name>
<a:Code>TSEGCRISUBCAT</a:Code>
<a:CreationDate>1422954629</a:CreationDate>
<a:Creator>U001107</a:Creator>
<a:ModificationDate>1584624853</a:ModificationDate>
<a:Modifier>U008652</a:Modifier>
<a:Comment>A Criteria Sub-Category provides a second level of grouping for Segmentation Criteria used in the Segment Rule editor.
A Sub-Category is supported at a specific Granularity (i.e. Contract, Contract/Section...), see TSEGCRIGRAN.
It contains a set of Criteria and belongs to a single Category.</a:Comment>
