<o:Table Id="o351">
<a:ObjectID>EE0E6708-8268-475B-8FD1-33A6F3E19FDC</a:ObjectID>
<a:Name>Segmentation&#39;s Included Section Accounting Statuses</a:Name>
<a:Code>TSEG2SECACCSTS</a:Code>
<a:CreationDate>1422954629</a:CreationDate>
<a:Creator>U001107</a:Creator>
<a:ModificationDate>1584624853</a:ModificationDate>
<a:Modifier>U008652</a:Modifier>
<a:Comment>This table defines the scope of Section Accounting Statuses on which a Segmentation is applied.
It is filled only in case of custom Section Accounting Status scope (see ALLSECACCSTS_B field of the TSEGMENTATION table).
Otherwise, all Section accounting statuses are considered.</a:Comment>
