<o:Table Id="o353">
<a:ObjectID>AD0410D0-4D19-4917-BD3F-96C6CC38FDC0</a:ObjectID>
<a:Name>Segmentation to export to the UW</a:Name>
<a:Code>TUWEXPORT</a:Code>
<a:CreationDate>1422954629</a:CreationDate>
<a:Creator>U001107</a:Creator>
<a:ModificationDate>1584624853</a:ModificationDate>
<a:Modifier>U008652</a:Modifier>
<a:Comment>This table defines which segmentation types has to be exported to the UW, which are the target DB columns for the code and label, and which table to use reagrding the scope of the segmentation (TUWSEC or TUWRETSEC) 
In order to be taken into account, the segmetnation types must be flagged as to be exported</a:Comment>
<a:TotalSavingCurrency/>
