<o:Table Id="o387">
<a:ObjectID>C5F88A80-1F9B-4FA8-9B88-039B473BF730</a:ObjectID>
<a:Name>To store IFRS17 expense ratio</a:Name>
<a:Code>TEXPRAT</a:Code>
<a:CreationDate>1538143502</a:CreationDate>
<a:Creator>u002559</a:Creator>
<a:ModificationDate>1709210836</a:ModificationDate>
<a:Modifier>frxb403</a:Modifier>
<a:Comment>28/09/2018 - REQ.03.4 - To store IFRS17 expenses ratios.
Table is used to store expense ratio(Acquisition Ratio, Maintenance Ratio). 
Key column used are  
   SSD_CF, ESB_CF, SEG_NF, CTRNAT_CT, NORME_CF,  CLODAT_D, PER_CF</a:Comment>
<a:TotalSavingCurrency/>
